```plantuml
@startuml arkaneshiro_Sound-Zone

[App] as app
[Redux Store] as store
[API Client] as api
[Cloudinary] as cloudinary
[Authentication] as auth
[Sound Management] as sound
[User Management] as user
[Search] as search

app --> store : uses
app --> api : calls
app --> cloudinary : uploads/retrieves media
app --> auth : manages authentication
app --> sound : manages sounds
app --> user : manages users
app --> search : performs searches

store --> api : dispatches actions
store --> auth : stores auth state
store --> sound : stores sound state
store --> user : stores user state

auth --> api : authenticates
sound --> api : fetches/updates sounds
user --> api : fetches/updates users
search --> api : queries users/sounds

api --> cloudinary : retrieves media URLs

@enduml
```